            <characteristic name="Rules" typeId="4834-43a9-1c93-9062">**Survey the Land**: Enemy models cannot use the INFILTRATOR Keyword to deploy within 16” of a model with this Keyword unless they are in their own side’s deployment zone.</characteristic>
